---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { site } from '../config/site';
---

<Base
  title={`Photo & Logo Credits | ${site.name}`}
  description="Attribution for photographs and logos used on the Dekson ITI website."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <div class="hangs">
      <p class="kicker">Attribution</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900">Photo &amp; Logo Credits</h1>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-10">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900">Photographs</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
        All photographs on this website — the campus, buildings, workshops, labs, computer lab,
        auditorium and grounds — were taken at {site.name}, Babhulgaon, Akola, and are the property
        of the institute.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900">Logos &amp; affiliation marks</h2>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
        <li class="border-b border-stone-200 pb-4">
          <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Deksons Institutes logo</span> — the property of
          Shri Akola Gujarati Samaj Trust.
        </li>
        <li class="border-b border-stone-200 pb-4">
          <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">Skill India</span> — trademark of the Ministry of
          Skill Development &amp; Entrepreneurship, Government of India. Shown to indicate the
          institute's genuine affiliation. Logo file via
          <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Skill_India_Logo.jpg" rel="noopener nofollow" class="underline hover:text-navy-700">Wikimedia Commons</a> (CC0).
        </li>
        <li class="border-b border-stone-200 pb-4">
          <span class="font-semibold text-stone-900">ITI / NCVT mark</span> — mark of the Directorate
          General of Training, Government of India. Shown to indicate genuine affiliation. Logo file via
          <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Industrial_Training_Institute_logo.jpg" rel="noopener nofollow" class="underline hover:text-navy-700">Wikimedia Commons</a> (CC BY-SA 4.0).
        </li>
        <li>
          The names and marks of DGT, NCVT and DVET belong to their respective government bodies and
          are used only to state the institute's genuine affiliation and recognition.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-900">Icons &amp; fonts</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-600">
        Interface icons are from <a href="https://lucide.dev" rel="noopener nofollow" class="underline hover:text-navy-700">Lucide</a> (ISC licence).
        Typefaces are Source Serif 4, Inter and Mukta, all open-source via Google Fonts.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
